    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold strictly as-is, likely best suited as a project car or a source for parts. The engine currently runs roughly and the transmission exhibits significant slipping, meaning it will likely require a tow from the lot. The exterior suffers from extensive rust along the rocker panels, several large dents, and heavily faded paint. Inside, the cabin shows heavy wear with torn upholstery, a cracked dashboard, and non-functional air conditioning. It needs substantial mechanical and cosmetic work to be roadworthy again.",
